[[ Test environment info ]]

Prerequisites: 
    - add appropriate "initialization-host" "operation-host" definitions to /etc/hosts
    - change fields in /etc/ssl/openssl.cnf policy_match section to "optional"
    instead of "required" to avoid openssl bug in ASN1 type matching

$ cd sb
$ ./inst.sh

The script will:
- generate 2 test CAs
- create credentials for SB simulator services and ECE
- configure apache accordingly

Components are installed to /test.
